soot.coffi

Class exception_table_entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.coffi.exception_table_entry

  •  class exception_table_entry
extends java.lang.Object
    An entry in some code's exception table; describes an exception handler and the code it protects.
    See Also:
    Code_attribute
